platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Originally released in 2000, Final Fantasy IX set a new standard for the seriesand its still astoundingly impressive. Its a perfect blend of beloved RPG elements from previous entries and modernized battle encounters. As you make your way through the storys twists and turns, youll encounter unforgettable characters, frighteningly powerful enemies, and a wonderful fantasy world to explore.
